features: Perfectly sized to remove hair in small or hard to reach areas. Stainless Steel blade is gentle on skin for quick and pain-free brow shaping.
Stainless steel blades are durable and easy to clean.
For optimal performance, replace razor blades every 2-3 months or as needed.
3 replacement blades include with Safety cap for safe storage.

How to Use: Remove cap from tool, hold the brow razor at an angle and with light pressure, apply short, feathery strokes downward to remove unwanted hair. To avoid irritation, move in the direction of hair growth. Use once per week. For optimal performance, replace razor blades every 2-3 months or as needed. To replace blades, pinch the plastic edge and pull out from tool. If blade is stuck, slowly wiggle from side to side until loose. Slide new blade in and safely discard used blade.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: KEY FEATURES: Perfectly sized to remove hair in small or hard to reach areas. Stainless Steel blade is gentle on skin for quick and pain-free brow shaping. Stainless steel blades are sanitary, durable and easy to clean. For optimal performance, replace razor blades every 2-3 months or as needed; 3 replacement blades included. Safety cap included for safe storage. Brow Razor HOW TO USE: Remove cap from tool, hold the brow razor at an angle and with light pressure, apply short, feathery strokes downward to remove unwanted hair.To avoid irritation, move in the direction of hair growth. Use once per week. Do not use more than 3 times per area.For optimal performance, replace razor blades every 2-3 months or as needed.Clean razor with an alcohol wipe before and after each use. Once dry, replace cap and store.To replace blades, pinch the plastic edge and pull out from tool. If blade is stuck, slowly wiggle from side to side until loose. Slide new blade in and safely discard of used blade. Handle with care, blade is sharp. TOOL CARE: Clean with alcohol to prevent infection and bacteria build-up before and after each use. Place the cap back on the razors after use and store in a dry place. Handle razor with care, blade is sharp.

Perfect Your Brow Routine TRIM Tweezerman's Brow Scissors and Brush are ergonomically designed to comfortably fit everyone’s hands. Start your brow grooming with the included spoolie to brush hairs up and follow with the Brow Scissors to trim long hairs. SHAPE Outline your desired brow shape with Tweezerman’s Brow Brushes. Continue by removing any hair outside of your brow outline using the Slant and Point Tweezers. These tweezers are the perfect combo to tweeze strays and baby fine hairs. All of Tweezerman's tweezers are hand-filed by trained professionals to ensure best quality. SCULPT After grooming, define your brows with Tweezerman’s new brow brushes and your favorite cosmetic products. Our brush collection features different brushes made with all brow types in mind for any of your brow shaping needs. CARE Be sure to finish your routine by cleaning all of your tools to ensure cleanliness and longevity. All of Tweezerman's tools are easy to clean with alcohol, so they are perfect for grooming at home or to bring to the salon.

About The Brand Tweezerman has been shaping beauty routines for over 40 years, bringing high quality and reliable beauty tools to both professional and at-home spaces. With a focus on precision and craftsmanship, our tools deliver expert results every time. Built to last, all of our tools are easy to clean with alcohol, so they are perfect for grooming at home or to bring to the salon. Designed with everyone in mind, our wide range of products can be used across all ages, different hair types, skin textures, and complexions.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice eyebrow razor and comes with extra blades
reviews.reviewText: Tweezerman is quite well-known, so thought this would be a good buy. Although it arrived a few weeks late, the packaging was nice, and the razor arm is very sturdy. The blades are very small but very sharp. They are great to have when you need a little touch-up in between getting your eyebrows done. I like this product and use it when i need it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I had been ordering the longer blades for trimming and edging. I'm so glad I read through the Amazon Reviews. One of the reviewers mentioned this gadget for shaving. This one is PERFECT for mustache, goatees, and simply edge trimming. Also, comes with extra blades! Be sure to rinse after every use, dry it (I use one of those compressed air cans to ensure it is completely dry). I then dampen the blade a bit with Johnson's baby oil - this will keep your blade sharp and will last you a lot longer!

reviews.reviewText: Very sharp blades, good size. Didn’t scrape skin like many of plastic disposable ones do. Removed all hairs on first try without fail.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on August 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve tried a couple of different ones including a battery-operated razor and one a biodegradable plastic handle. The battery one kept falling apart and cut my skin up. The razor on the biodegradable one was blunt on arrival and hurt my skin. I figured I’d invest in Tweezerman and I’m not disappointed. The size is perfect to work around my microbladed eyebrows and tidy up any strays. The razor is sharp but comfortable on my skin. I also use it on my upper lip and chin.Highly recommended! Also love the metal handle and option for replacement blades!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on July 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Quite a sharp and long lasting blade (even comes with 3 extra blades). Don’t expect to be able to use this without shaving cream as it can get stuck on hairs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on October 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been buying disposable razors to shape my eyebrows for a few years now. Whilst it’s absolutely my preferred method, I’ve always encountered an issue one way or another, regardless of what brand I’ve used. I’d end up covered in bleeding nicks then days of tiny scabs (one of which has actually left a scar), or it wouldn’t shave ‘cleanly’, leaving little random stubbles that the razor just refused to shift, or it would go blunt within seconds of use.This razor? It’s like a dream. I haven’t once nicked the skin, it shaves cleanly and even removes pesky stubble when tidying the brows up, it stays sharp, has a ‘luxury’ brand feel to it with high quality materials, and it’s lightweight, fitting nicely in my makeup bag.My only regret is that I didn’t discover it sooner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Easy to use and also very sharp plus extra replacement heads
